---
title: Sticky Mango Glazed Tofu and Stir-Fried Veg with Korma Spiced Rice
description: Our Sticky Mango Glazed Tofu and Stir-Fried Veg is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R22_W35_UK_V15383-4_Main__1low-45c0bac9.jpg
